<h1>What is Food for My Neighbors About?</h1>
<p>Welcome to a social platform geared towards learning how to live a more sustainable life that is in tune with the Earth's natural abundance.  This site is also for sharing all types of foods that build and grow our bodies, minds, and community.  We are all about food for thought, food for well-being, and food for our souls.

Take some time to browse the site and find #FoodIsFree locations, Farmer's markets, gardening tips/tricks, hand/homemade items, and permaculture ideas.  Our goal is to help our neighbors live a healthier, simpler, and more sustainable life.</p>
<p><center>GET OUT, SOCIALIZE WITH YOUR NEIGHBORS, AND PLANT!</p></center>
